// import 'src/App.css';
import React from 'react';
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import { CardActionArea } from '@mui/material';
import { Button, Grid, Grow, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
import '../style/leader.css';
import '../style/cards.css'
import Leaderboard from '../pages/leaderboard';
import Trajectory from '../pages/trajectory';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'
import CardMedia from '@mui/material/CardMedia';



function Home() {
  const navigate = useNavigate(); // Initialize the useNavigate hook

  const navigateToStatistic = () => {
    navigate('/statistics'); // Navigate to the specified route
  };
  const navigateToTrajectory = () => {
    navigate('/trajectory'); // Navigate to the specified route
  };
  const navigateToLeaderboard = () => {
    navigate('/leaderboard'); // Navigate to the specified route
  };
    
    return (
        <Box component="main" sx={{flexGrow: 1, p:3}}>
            <Grid>
              <Grid item md={2}>
                <Stack spacing={2} direction="row">
                  <Card className='cards' onClick={navigateToStatistic} style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                      <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" color="white">
                        FASTEST LAP
                      </Typography>
                      </CardContent>                     
                    </CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent>
                      <Typography color="white" variant='body2'>
                        1:23:30
                      </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>
                  
                 
                  <Card className='cards' style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" color="white">
                          FASTEST MODEL NAME
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="white" >
                          TEAM DEEPRACER
                        </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                  </Card>

                  <Card className='cards' style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" color="white">
                          TRAJECTORY 
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="white">
                      <CardMedia
                        component="img"
                        alt="Car Trajectory"
                        height="140"
                        image="../src/assets/Trajec.png"
                      />
                    </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>

                  <Card className='cards' style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                    <CardActionArea>
                      <CardContent>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" color="white">
                          Model Name
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="white">
                        </Typography>
                      </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                  </Card>
                </Stack>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>

            {/* The code below is where the leaderboard will be located */}
            <Box height={20} />
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={8}>
                <Card sx={{height: 60 + "vh"}} onClick={navigateToLeaderboard} style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                  <CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent>
                    <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                        LeaderBoard
                    </Typography>
                      {/*<Leaderboard /> {/* Calls the leaderboard.js which incorporates leaderboard.jsx*/}
                    </CardContent>
                    </CardActionArea>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Card sx={{height: 60 + "vh"}} className='cards-two' onClick={navigateToTrajectory} style={{backgroundColor: '#5E35A7'}}>
                  <CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent>
                    <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                          Trajectory
                    </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                  </CardActionArea>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
    );
}

export default Home;
